      "content": "thanks. though it feels like you're saying the solar thing is obviously better since u called it a \"clear step toward a greener future.\" isn't the economic impact on the coal towns just as big of a deal as the environmental stuff? like, what are the actual arguments from the people who think this bill is a mistake?",
